Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
Is this the first time here？ I'm excited.
Ah. I think I can enjoy it.
Rinko
What shall we do for fun today？
Don't get too enthusiastic.
Rinko
I'm here again. Hehe .... I want to play a lot today.
Yeah. Let's have as much fun as we can.
Rinko
You didn't play enough, did you？
Actually....
Rinko
Let's thoroughly hang out.
Okay.
Rinko
30 Knots, that was fun. Let's do it again.
Oh, okay.
Rinko
I'm pretty sure there's some kind of winning formula for 30 knots, right？
Yeah, I remember there was some kind of number you could say first.
Rinko
The game "Daruma-san fell over" is still funny at my age.
That was really unexpected.
Rinko
When playing Daruma-san fell over, there are two types of people, those who go forward and those who wait behind.
Oh, I know what you mean.
Rinko
Ah, that was fun. Rinko might be better at guiding.
I think you might be right.
Rinko
Watermelon is a vegetable .... isn't it？ I don't care what it is as long as it tastes good.
Huh, that's true, if you ask me.
Rinko
Catching marshmallows was probably more difficult than I thought. But it made me enthusiastic.
Let's do it again.
Rinko
I heard that there are many ways to eat marshmallows. They also contain collagen, which is good for your beauty.
Wow, I didn't know that.
Kohayakawa
It takes a lot of concentration to play darts, doesn't it？ The better you get, the more addicted you might get！
Yeah. I think I'll practice more, too.
Rinko
There are many rules for darts, aren't there？ I guess the more knowledgeable you are, the more fun it is.
Let's start with the score calculation. I know it sounds like a lot of work, but I'm going to try ....
Rinko
The speed... it makes you mad, doesn't it？ Both of us have desperate faces.
Hahaha, but that's the funny part, isn't it？
Rinko
There's a local rule for speed, too. It's so complicated, why don't we just all use the same rules？
Yeah, that happens in other games too.
Rinko
What is it about soap bubbles that makes them so relaxing？
Children and adults are the same in this way.
Rinko
When making soap bubbles, if you add sugar or hyaluronic acid, it will be harder to break.
hyaluronic acid.... hm....
Rinko
This looks so easy when you watch it on TV, but it's hard when you try it yourself.
It keeps you on the edge of your seat and makes you excited, doesn't it？
Rinko
I heard that the person who came up with this game is some kind of famous person？ Did you know that？
hm....is that so？
Rinko
This game is so simple, but why do I get so excited about it？
It's a well-made game.
Rinko
Well, doesn't this look like we're a couple flirting？
Yes .... might be right.
Rinko
Space agent, that was interesting. I'll remember it well.
Me too！
Rinko
Isn't this kind of game like the basic arcade game？
It's hard to play at home, isn't it？ Probably so.
Rinko
I thought it was just a matter of selecting a panel, so I let my guard down. It takes a lot of thinking.
I guess both intuition and calculation are needed.
Rinko
If you can connect the panels well, you might want to do a victory pose.
Suddenly you feel empowered.
Rinko
When you have to choose between two options.... I lose.
Yeah, that's where you need to use your head.
Rinko
Ah.... it was my chance to win the jackpot.
So frustrating, let's try again.
Rinko
The moment you win the jackpot is a great feeling, isn't it？ I'm going to be addicted.
I was on the edge of my seat and it felt like a long time before the spinning stopped.
Rinko
Grand Cross was interesting, wasn't it？ I wonder if there are any more tips or tricks？
▲小早川＊▲, you seem to be good at finding things like that.
Rinko
I didn't think I'd be that nervous during the jackpot chance.
Really. It's a shame I missed it, though.
Rinko
That was a great jackpot for Grand Cross！ I was so excited to be in a celebratory mood.
I really want to taste that victory again and again.
Rinko
That was interesting. Doesn't Fortune Trinity feel like a bit of a trip？
You can see a lot of different world heritage sites.
Rinko
Jackpot, I knew you would make it！
My hands are sweating！ I guess it was that kind of thing.
Rinko
Fortune Trinity's jackpot is nice. I like the way the medals come out in time with the sound.
I'd like to see that again.
Rinko
The Anima Lotta Anima are cute, aren't they？ I think Rinko likes the cat-like ones the best.
Which one is the cat-like one...？
Rinko
I thought I'd get the jackpot chance in Anima Lotta. The number of balls was amazing, too.
The light effects were beautiful, weren't they？
Rinko
I'm glad I won the jackpot on Anima Lotta. The performance was beautiful, and I'm satisfied.
Okay, Let's watch it again.
Rinko
Jackpot chances make my shoulders tense up.
Even if you don't win, you can still have fun just watching.
Rinko
I wish I could have saved that jackpot chance. .... Too bad.
I'm sure you'll be fine next time.
Rinko
Did you see when I won the jackpot？ I'm so happy, I think I'm dreaming.
Me too！ It's burned into my memory.
Rinko
When you win a jackpot, you want to brag about it out loud to everyone.
Yeah. That's kind of impressive.
Rinko
I think I like medal games because I feel that they are unique to arcade games.
I enjoyed it a lot too.
Rinko
I think medal games are pretty fun. Gaming is good, but I think I'll get into this too.
It looks like I'll be getting more and more addicted to arcade games.
Rinko
It was a great harvest. We got a lot of medals, and the performance was sparkling and spectacular.
I wish it was always like this.
Rinko
We didn't get many medals out of it, but the game was fun.
Yeah. But if I could get a lot of medals out of that, I wouldn't complain.
Rinko
That was really fun. Rinko had a great time, but what about you？
Of course it was fun.
Rinko
I've gotten too carried away. Did Rinko get excited all by herself？
No, not at all. I got carried away too.
Rinko
Time flies so fast, doesn't it？ I hate that it's already over.
Truly. I wish I could play more.
Rinko
That was great. It was so much fun that I want to live here. Heh.
It was worth the trip.
Rinko
Oh, that was fun. I'm sure it's because I'm with you that it's so much fun.
Haha, that's a nice thing to say.
Rinko
Rinko, it's addictive. I'll definitely come back again.
Ah.
Rinko
Hey, when are you coming next？ You should come as soon as possible.
Yeah.
Rinko
But .... it's a bit frustrating. I'll get my revenge next time！
He's really into it.
Rinko
But this result doesn't make sense to me.
Please don't get too heated.
Rinko
But hey, if I'd worked harder there.... I'll do some research when I get home.
.... you are surprisingly studious.
Okay, scratch that.
Silver, maybe. I'd like to make a good guess here.
Whoa！ It's a no-lose gold scratch.
Oh, platinum！ I'm going for the high price.
This is the premiere of the .... legend！ It's kind of divine.
Rinko
Isn't it to the right？
Rinko
I think it's left....
Rinko
Hm.. the middle one is suspicious.
Rinko
Um... I'm lost..
Rinko
Hmm, I don't know. I'll leave it to you.
Rinko
Rinko believes in you！
I did it！ I won！
Oh！ I'm glad I listened to ▲小早川＊▲.
Alright！Maybe I got the message from ▲小早川＊▲.
Oh, I guess I missed ....
I should have trusted ▲小早川＊▲'s intuition.
